txt.en: Wandering glooms can be found along the river Gladden.\n\nYou should defeat wandering glooms.
You have defeated many wandering glooms along the river Gladden, making the Vales of Anduin safer.
A strange darkness has come to the Vales of Anduin. Wandering glooms move along the river Gladden. These creatures should be defeated if the Vales are to remain safe.
Wandering glooms move along the river Gladden.
